author: Olivia Willis
title: Can you get coronavirus twice? What we know so far about COVID-19 and immunity
description: People infected with COVID-19 are likely to generate some immunity, but it's unclear for how long.
content:
Your immune system is like your own personal army: a vast network of cells, tissues and organs that coordinate your body's defences against illness and disease.
